<div class="com-share" data-id="26165" data-title="《百货公司不景气，拉来坪效更高的丝芙兰提升收益》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/26165/medium/26165.jpg?1461897603" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/26165.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
